name: Tiyanak
description: The Tiyanak is a small humanoid monster in Philippine mythology which pretends to be an innocent baby before attacking humans.t disguises itself as a baby abandoned in the forest or in the field. It wails loudly to attract a passerby and when picked up it sheds its disguise like a snake shedding its old skin, revealing its true form, and kills the victim by biting and mauling.
